    "6 (see Methods -Cluster characterizations).",
    "HPCs associated with better survival outcomes show positive correlations with being severe to moderate lymphocytic infiltration and RNASeq signatures of tumor infiltrating leukocytes (TIL), lymphocyte infiltration signature score, T-cell receptors (TCR), and macrophage regulation; and show over-representations of inflammatory, dead, and neoplastic cells.",
